model.name: Starbuck1990 - EGF binding and trafficking dynamics in Fibroblast

body.pre: mathematical model, with accompanying quantitative experimental data, for binding and trafficking properties of the epidermal growth factor (EGF) receptor on B82 fibroblasts, and propose a theoretical dependence of cell proliferation rate on these properties. Model encoded by Matthieu Maire adn submitted to BioModels by Krishna Kumar Tiwari.
